reviewText: She doesn't like it as much as the others

The HD download didn't work at all.  I followed the instructions, asked to download via iTunes and somehow the process didn't work.  The fox site gave me an error number to look up on iTurnes, but that didn't produce any results.  I am very disappointed - I have spent money and have nothing to show for it.  I do hope the rest of you are bying this to use with a DVD player.
